Title: 30 Door Key
Writer: Jerzy Skolimowski (scenario), Józef Skolimowski (scenario), Michal Skolimowski (scenario), Witold Gombrowicz (based on the novel by), Michael Sarne (scenario consultant)
Actors: Iain Glen, Robert Stephens, Crispin Glover, Judith Godrèche
Plot: A young writer in 1939 Warsaw faces the conflict of acting his age or relapsing into childhood during the brink of World War II.
